profile.profileName: [Roundabout Theater Company, New York, NY, USA] Performance organization
profile.profileDescription: This profile configures CollectiveAccess for use as an archive for images, documents, objects, video and oral history. It is intended for use by the Roundabout Theater Company (http://www.roundabouttheater.org)
